        <h2 class="mb-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
          Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0)
        </h2>
        
        <p class="mb-4 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          <strong>Copyright (c) 2025 Free DevTools</strong>
        </p>
        
        <p class="mb-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy of this content and associated materials (the "Content"), to share, copy, distribute, and adapt the Content for any purpose, even commercially, subject to the following condition:
