          You must give appropriate credit to Free DevTools, provide a link to the license, and indicate if changes were made. You may do so in any reasonable manner, but not in a way that suggests Free DevTools endorses you or your use.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
          No Additional Restrictions
        </h3>
        <p class="mb-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">
          You may not apply legal terms or technological measures that legally restrict others from doing anything the license permits.
        </p>
        
        <h3 class="mb-3 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
          Disclaimer
